# One-off dev/scrape scripts — exclude from the Vercel upload…
*.mjs
# …but KEEP build-critical config files (they are also .mjs).
# Without postcss.config.mjs, Tailwind v4's `@import "tailwindcss"` is never
# processed → no CSS is generated and the build fails.
!postcss.config.mjs
!eslint.config.mjs

# NOTE: do NOT ignore `public/` — it holds logo.png and /images/** used
# across Nav, Footer, builders, fabrics, and product galleries.
